OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Frather cloudy evening but some
OL,7,Fbrightness in places. Remaining dry
OL,8,Fovernight with lengthening clear
OL,9,Fspells. A mild night. Light
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA largely dry day with some
OL,13,Fsunshine but cloudier across Moray.
OL,14,FCloudier with a little rain early in
OL,15,Fthe evening. Warm in the south.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,18,Fand bright with plenty of sunshine
OL,19,Fduring this period. Becoming
OL,20,Fincreasingly warm in general, but
OL,21,Fcooler at times along the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
